The '''Third Atrisian period''' was a historical period on the planet [[Atrisia/Legends|Atrisia]], also known as Kitel Phard. It coincided with at least a part of the [[Sidereal Era]], a fairly peaceable era for the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. The reign of the 54th Atrisian [[Emperor/Legends|emperor]], [[Uueg Tching]] occurred during this era, which saw the practical unification of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] under his rule. Uueg's ''[[Sayings]]'' were composed at this time.

